    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs roughly, the transmission has noticeable slippage, and there are several fluid leaks that need immediate addressing. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels, multiple large dents, and the clear coat is failing across most surfaces. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system, making this an ideal candidate for a dedicated project car or a parts donor.",
