      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a machine that doesn't just transport you, but transcends the ordinary. This isn't merely a car; it's a preserved moment of automotive perfection, finished in a coat of paint so deep it feels like looking into a still lake at midnight. Every curve of its sculpted body tells a story of elegance and speed, while the interior welcomes you with the scent of fine leather and the promise of open-road freedom. To drive it is to conduct a mechanical symphony, a seamless dance between man and machine that feels as fresh today as the moment it first touched the asphalt. This is a rare opportunity to own a piece of rolling art that demands attention and rewards the soul.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
